title: Slow Cooker Pineapple Salsa Chicken aka Mexican Delight
directions: Puts all ingredients in Slow Cooker and cook on high for 4-6 hours or low for 6-8 hours or until chicken shreds easily.
When I use frozen chicken I start it out on high for 3 hours and then turn it down to low for 3 more hours.
